        "ROB_BELMONT_BODY_MORRIS_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESC": "Comme<color=#3060FF>Belmont</color>, obtenez une relique sacrée.",
        "ROB_BELMONT_BODY_JULIUS_UNLOCKABLE_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "<color=#3060FF>Belmont</color>: Dawn of Sorrow",
